snippet.textDisplay:
Hi Linda 😊
You should video a game of “sniffer dog” with Tucker. I used to play this game with my dogs before they passed away. I would hide them in a room (they would know what was happening) and hide cubes of cheese around the house or room. I would then let them out and give each dog a cube of cheese so they k ow what scent to sniff out. my staffy Dallas was a pro. Her sniffer would be going full steam lolz 😂
I miss having a dog so much. I’m a crazy cat lady now hahaha 😻❤️😜
